<div class="container centered">
  <h1 class="title">Pods</h1>
</div>

<div class="story-section center-block">
  <h2>About</h2>
  <div class="row">
    <div class="body-text">
      <p>At SZW we have a decentralized power structure that allows anyone to be a leader of their own ‘pod’ and create their own project. We call them pods to highlight the idea that they are connected to a larger whole even though they can be distinct entities in themselves. Pods often come in and out of rotation with their leadership are often turn into long-term projects for members.</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="row">
    <% @projects.order('created_at DESC').each do |project| %>
      <div class="col-md-4 mx-auto story-section">
        <div class="pod-title">
          <h3><%=project.title%></h3>
        </div>
        <div class="img-responsive">
          <%=image_tag project.picture.url.to_s, class: "pod-img rounded"%>
        </div>
      </div>
    <%end%>
  </div>

